## Codebase Discoveries
- KEY FINDING: ADK auto-instrument re-instruments nested AgentTool runners ->
  detached sub-trace, NOT a nested subtree. Explicit-plugin mode (plugin only
  on the outer runner) stays one clean trace because the nested runner has no
  plugin. Recorded to memory (project_adk_agenttool_detached_trace). Open
  question for the user: suppress nested-runner instrumentation / propagate
  context so AgentTool nests, or document the detached trace?
- weave.init accepts a custom SpanProcessor publicly (settings.genai
  .spanProcessor: 'batch'|'simple'|SpanProcessor); buildSpanProcessor returns
  it verbatim and bypasses buildOtlpExporter -> no network export.

